AC

"AC" is your armor class.  It is a number from -100 to 100, roughly
defined as follows:


  AC  Roughly equivalent to
-----------------------------------------------------------
  100  Naked person (No armour)
    0  Moderatly Armoured (Plate mail, and "two shields") 
 -100  Completely Armoured

The score command displays your armor class as a number such as 78/10;
this means 78 on a scale from -100 to 100

See also: SCORE
