CLERIC

Clerics are the priest class of Deimos.  They live spiritual lives and focus on protecting 
and healing others through magical means.  They are devoted to whichever God they serve.  
Clerics can also be good or evil, depending on their God.  What is important to classify 
a cleric different from a mage is the magic each uses.  Clerics themselves have very little 
offensive magic and it used as a last resort in thier defense.

Ultimate: Manashield
See Also: PRACTICE, SKILLCLERIC, ULTIMATE
#
MAGE

Mages are the wielders of powerful destructive magic.  As they are seekers of changing elements 
and not maintaining order through magic, they do not dabble into the healing arts.  Mages 
spend many years studying the arcane arts of destructive magic and can wreak havoc on their enemies
with their powerful spells of destruction.

Ultimate: Novastorm
